title: EU needs its own Ukraine peace plans, says defense commissioner
description: Andrius Kubilius tells POLITICO the bloc needs to be more proactive on its own defense, "in case Article 5 suddenly is not implemented."
content: The former Lithuanian prime minister has been the bloc's first defense commissioner for a year a sign of how much has changed in the EU as it wakes up to the threat posed by Russia and ramps up its r… [+1918 chars]
